FBIS4-10362 "drlat070_q_94002" FBIS-LAT-94-070 Daily Report 8 Apr 1994 Paraguay Chamber of Deputies To Interrogate Minister Chamber of Deputies To Interrogate Minister PY0804182794 Asuncion ABC COLOR in Spanish 8 Apr 94 p 2 PY0804182794 Asuncion ABC COLOR Spanish BFN [Excerpt] The Chamber of Deputies yesterday decided by a wide margin to approve a request presented by Deputy Luis Alberto Mauro to interrogate Justice and Labor Minister Juan Manuel Morales. The questionnaire the minister will have to answer has, in principle, nine questions, but other questions may be added during the questioning session. Colorado Party followers tried to prevent the interrogation, but the opposition remained firm and imposed their majority. [passage omitted]
